name: Rosemary for Remembrance
description:
//There’s rosemary, that’s for remembrance and there is pansies, that’s for thoughts...//

This is a true virtual reality NFT. If you have a VR headset, use Firefox or Firefox Reality to view, then click the VR button to experience from the inside. On browser, use mouse and WASD keys.

Please note that this is an updated version of OBJKT#80533, with no external dependencies.

Music by Emelie Waldken and Pascal Ruegger via Creative Commons
